          <trans-unit id="vFlAzEQ" resname="main.projets.descIA">
            <source>main.projets.descIA</source>
            <target>
              During my training, I created an AI that analyzed news reports and guessed the theme using a list of words
              I gave it in Java. I then had it analyze 500 news reports to test it, and it had a success rate of nearly 80%.
            </target>
          </trans-unit>
