          <trans-unit id="iyGEY.z" resname="main.projets.descBD">
            <source>main.projets.descBD</source>
            <target>
              During my training, I cleaned up a Nutriscore database that contained duplicates and impossible values. I
              then extracted some interesting data to create graphs explaining what Nutriscore is.
            </target>
          </trans-unit>
          <trans-unit id="y5XVSjn" resname="main.projets.titleEvent">
