          </trans-unit>
          <trans-unit id="uMBJnUO" resname="main.projets.descEvent">
            <source>main.projets.descEvent</source>
            <target>
              During my training, I participated in a group project with five other students to create software that
              helps event organizers. This taught me the importance of communication in group work. We can save a lot
              of time by coordinating properly. I was responsible for designing UML diagrams and sequence diagrams
              illustrating the application code, which gave me experience in thinking about how an IT service should
              function properly. I also wrote the Java model code.
            </target>
          </trans-unit>
          <trans-unit id="FfnCPam" resname="main.projets.titleMusee">
            <source>main.projets.titleMusee</source>
            <target>Museum visit application development</target>
          </trans-unit>
          <trans-unit id="4NVpnz4" resname="main.projets.descMusee">
            <source>main.projets.descMusee</source>
            <target>During another student project in a team of seven, I participated in the development of an
                    application used to create fictional museum itineraries for those who don't have time to visit
                    everything. I was able to gain more experience working with a project manager and discovering the
                    NextJS framework. I handled various tasks such as the TypeScript model, the design and ergonomics
                    of the application, the creation of diagrams, and bug fixes.</target>
          </trans-unit>
          <trans-unit id="lNW0AMH" resname="main.projets.titleAppUp">
            <source>main.projets.titleAppUp</source>
