          </trans-unit>
          <trans-unit id="JI3qzPG" resname="main.projets.descAppUp">
            <source>main.projets.descAppUp</source>
            <target>Later in my BUT2, I also improved an internship search application provided by IUT teachers. It was
                    a group project involving five people. It showed me the consequences of poor work and how to remedy
                    it. I was responsible for improving the database
                    and the server side using the Symfony framework.</target>
          </trans-unit>
